  "title": "Mortgage Loans Sales (Retail Banking)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assess and review existing housing loan accounts for conversion eligibility</li>\n  <li>Prepare and submit loan conversion cases for credit approval</li>\n  <li>Draft and verify customer loan conversion offer letters</li>\n  <li>Monitor and follow up on approved conversions, including handling any rework of offer letters</li>\n  <li>Conduct interviews with customers regarding loan redemption</li>\n  <li>Support management and department initiatives through ad-hoc tasks and assignments</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 1-2 years of experience in a related role, preferably within consumer banking</li>\n  <li>Solid understanding of retail banking products, particularly in mortgage financing</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills, with the ability to engage and negotiate effectively across various stakeholders</li>\n  <li>Competent in Microsoft Office tools, with an aptitude for data handling and analysis</li>\n  <li>Demonstrates teamwork, service excellence, and the ability to work with speed and precision</li>\n  <li>Independent, self-motivated, and resourceful in resolving issues and meeting deadlines</li>\n</ul>",
